data.chText: 心态；思想状况；思想方法
data.enText: the particular attitude or way of thinking of a person or group

data.chText: 我无法理解足球流氓的心态。
data.enText: I cannot understand the mentality of football hooligans.

data.chText: 犯罪心态；种族聚居区的思想意识

example: he's got plenty of brains but no common sense

tr: a habitual or characteristic mental attitude that determines how you will interpret and respond to situations

value.def: Your mentality is your attitudes and your way of thinking.

example.ex: Running a business requires a very different mentality from being a salaried employee.
example.tran: 经营企业所要求具备的心态和上班族的心态截然不同。
